---
// src/components/Footer.astro
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-primary-900 text-white pt-16 pb-8">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12">
    
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-black tracking-tighter uppercase italic decoration-accent-500 underline underline-offset-4">iDECAL</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        Đơn vị chuyên sâu trong lĩnh vực cung cấp và thi công decal dán kính, phim cách nhiệt nhà kính chuyên nghiệp tại TP.HCM.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <h4 class="text-sm font-black uppercase text-accent-500 tracking-widest">Dịch vụ</h4>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-300">
        <li><a href="/dich-vu/decal-dan-kinh-van-phong" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Decal Văn Phòng</a></li>
        <li><a href="/dich-vu/phim-cach-nhiet" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Phim Cách Nhiệt</a></li>
        <li><a href="/dich-vu/decal-mo-3d" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Decal Mờ 3D</a></li>
        <li><a href="/dich-vu/decal-cat-chu" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Cắt Chữ & Logo</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <h4 class="text-sm font-black uppercase text-accent-500 tracking-widest">Hệ thống</h4>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-300">
        <li><a href="https://idecal.vn" target="_blank" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">idecal.vn</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://thicongdecal.pro" target="_blank" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">thicongdecal.pro</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://homedecal.vn" target="_blank" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">homedecal.vn</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <h4 class="text-sm font-black uppercase text-accent-500 tracking-widest">Liên hệ</h4>
      <div class="bg-primary-600/30 p-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/10">
        <p class="text-[10px] font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase mb-1">Hotline thi công</p>
        <a href="tel:086677040" class="text-2xl font-black text-white hover:text-accent-500 transition-colors">0866-77040</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-[10px] text-gray-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">
    <p>© {year} iDECAL - All Rights Reserved.</p>
    <p>Sản phẩm bởi iDecal Team.</p>
  </div>
</footer>
